OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain
OL,6,Fclearing to the east this evening
OL,7,Fallowing a brief drier and clearer
OL,8,Fspell to develop overnight. However
OL,9,Flater in the night, cloud and rain
OL,10,Fwill move back into the west. Rather
OL,11,Fmild overnight with winds easing
OL,12,Facross the south.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FOften cloudy and wet towards
OL,15,Fthe northwest, with the rain turning
OL,16,Fheavy and possibly thundery in places.
OL,17,FDrier and brighter towards the
OL,18,Fsoutheast where it will be feeling
OL,19,Fwarmer.
